5#ifndef V8_TRACING_CODE_TRACE_CONTEXT_H_
6#define V8_TRACING_CODE_TRACE_CONTEXT_H_
7
8#include <string>
9
10#include "protos/perfetto/trace/chrome/v8.pbzero.h"
11#include "src/base/compiler-specific.h"
12#include "src/objects/tagged.h"
13#include "src/tracing/code-data-source.h"
14
15namespace v8 {
16namespace internal {
17
18class Isolate;
19class Script;
20class SharedFunctionInfo;
21
22// Helper class to write V8 related trace packets.
23// Used to intern various types and to set common trace proto fields.
24class CodeTraceContext {
25 public:
26 CodeTraceContext(CodeDataSource::TraceContext::TracePacketHandle trace_packet,
27 CodeDataSourceIncrementalState* incremental_state)
28 : trace_packet_(std::move(trace_packet)),
29 incremental_state_(*incremental_state) {}
30
31 CodeTraceContext(CodeTraceContext&&) V8_NOEXCEPT = default;
32
33 ~CodeTraceContext() {
34 if (V8_UNLIKELY(incremental_state_.has_buffered_interned_data())) {
35 incremental_state_.FlushInternedData(trace_packet_);
36 }
37 }
38
39 uint64_t InternIsolate(Isolate& isolate) {
40 return incremental_state_.InternIsolate(isolate);
41 }
42
43 uint64_t InternJsScript(Isolate& isolate, Tagged<Script> script) {
44 return incremental_state_.InternJsScript(isolate, script);
45 }
46
47 uint64_t InternJsFunction(Isolate& isolate, Handle<SharedFunctionInfo> info,
48 uint64_t v8_js_script_iid, int line_num,
49 int column_num) {
50 return incremental_state_.InternJsFunction(isolate, info, v8_js_script_iid,
51 line_num, column_num);
52 }
53
54 uint64_t InternWasmScript(Isolate& isolate, int script_id,
55 const std::string& url) {
56 return incremental_state_.InternWasmScript(isolate, script_id, url);
57 }
58
59 perfetto::protos::pbzero::V8JsCode* set_v8_js_code() {
60 return trace_packet_->set_v8_js_code();
61 }
62
63 perfetto::protos::pbzero::V8InternalCode* set_v8_internal_code() {
64 return trace_packet_->set_v8_internal_code();
65 }
66
67 perfetto::protos::pbzero::V8WasmCode* set_v8_wasm_code() {
68 return trace_packet_->set_v8_wasm_code();
69 }
70
71 perfetto::protos::pbzero::V8RegExpCode* set_v8_reg_exp_code() {
72 return trace_packet_->set_v8_reg_exp_code();
73 }
74
75 perfetto::protos::pbzero::V8CodeMove* set_code_move() {
76 return trace_packet_->set_v8_code_move();
77 }
78
79 bool log_script_sources() const {
80 return incremental_state_.log_script_sources();
81 }
82
83 bool log_instructions() const {
84 return incremental_state_.log_instructions();
85 }
86
87 private:
88 CodeDataSource::TraceContext::TracePacketHandle trace_packet_;
89 CodeDataSourceIncrementalState& incremental_state_;
90};
91
92} // namespace internal
93} // namespace v8

95#endif // V8_TRACING_CODE_TRACE_CONTEXT_H_
